(newid(), 'http://localhost/projectinsight.webapp/api/help/model/taskpredecessor', '[u"

TaskPredecessor

Task Predecessor object defines relationships between tasks within projects.

NameDescriptionType
Duration Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Lead/Lag] - Whether the duration specified is lead time or lag time. Lead time means the task will start earlier by the amount of duration specified. Lag means the task will start later by the amount of duration specified.

Remarks: Default Property

 integer
Id Gets or sets the guid Id. guid
IdExternal Gets or sets the ProjectInsight.Models.Base.ApiModelBase.IdExternal object which allows the object to be saved with an associated external identification. Used primarily for integrations. IdExternal
IsLag Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Lead/Lag] - Whether the duration specified is lead time or lag time. Lead time means the task will start earlier by the amount of duration specified. Lag means the task will start later by the amount of duration specified.

Remarks: Default Property

 boolean
Predecessor Gets (read only) the Task - [Task] - Select a task or tasks that must come (predecessor) before this current task.

Remarks: Read Only

 Task
Predecessor_Id Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Task] - Select a task or tasks that must come (predecessor) before this current task.

Remarks: Default Property

 guid
PredecessorType Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Type] - The type of relationship:
Finish-to-Start = Predecessor finishes before this task starts
Finish-to-Finish = Predecessor and this task finish at the same time
Start-to-Start = Predecessor and this task start at the same time
Start-to-Finish = Predecessor starts when this task finishes.

Remarks: Default Property

 integer
SerializeType Get or Set if the Type should be serialized boolean
Task Gets (read only) the Task

Remarks: Read Only

 Task
Task_Id Gets or sets the NullableOfT guid
TaskPredecessorRefID Gets or sets the string reference or ID to use for looking up this task for a task predecessor relationship. Use this when uploading NEW tasks in bulk\, with predecessors\, because a GUID id is not established. There is a matching property on the TaskPredecessor object which can also be set in leiu of IDs which are not assigned yet. string
Type Gets or sets the string object type for external reference\, rest calls. string
